snippet.title: Pumpkin Jack: 8 Minutes of Gameplay | Gamescom 2020
snippet.description: Check out some exclusive gameplay of Pumpkin Jack, a spooky action platformer inspired by classic 3D adventure games of past generations, debuted during Gamescom 2020 presented by IGN.
